The '''Lig sword''' was a [[weapon]] used by the [[Kaleesh/Legends|Kaleesh]] of [[Kalee/Legends|Kalee]], named for the [[Lig]] tribe. A product of dedication and artistry, a Lig sword took several days to create. Lig swords began with a pointed tip, and the blade grew wider as it neared the pommel. They were commonly used for [[Mumuu/Legends|mumuu]] [[Hunting/Legends|hunting]].

During the [[Huk War]], Lig swords were mass-produced using new techniques and [[Metal/Legends|metals]], such as [[scatrium]] and [[Impervium/Legends|impervium]].

